Param Sant Huzur '''Kanwar Saheb''', born on 2 March 1948, is the present master of [[Radha Swami Satsang, Dinod]].<ref>[http://www.radhaswamidinod.org/lineage.htm Radhaswamidinod.org: Life of Param Sant Huzur Kanwar Saheb Maharaj]</ref> <ref>His name is Kanwar Singh. "Param Sant," "Huzur," and "Saheb" are honorifics.</ref>
[[File:Sant Kanwar Saheb at Bhiwani Ashram.JPG|thumb|Kanwar Saheb giving [[Satsang]] at Bhiwani Ashram. Picture also depicts previous five gurus of Radha Swami Satsang, Dinod]]. [[File:Sant Kanwar Saheb at Dinod Ashram.JPG|thumb|Kanwar Saheb on the way to deliver [[Satsang]] at Radha Swami Dinod Ashram.]] [[File:Sant Kanwar Saheb giving Satsang at Dinod Ashram.JPG|thumb|Kanwar Saheb getting ready to deliver [[Satsang]] at Radha Swami Dinod Ashram.]]
==Literature== Saheb has written several religious books, including:<ref>[http://www.radhaswamidinod.org/books.html Books published by RSSD]</ref> *''Satguru Prem'' *''Radhaswami Nij Naam Sada ki Mukti'' *''Jui Se Jahan'' *''Satguru Satsang (Adh Ghadi Ka)'' *''Pravachan Sangreh'' *''Satguru Gyanvahini'' *''Nirmal Bhakti'' *''Nirmal Dhara''
