'''Stefan Sarnowski''' (born in 1939-12 March 2014<ref>[http://www.nekrologi.net/kondolencje/stefan-sarnowski/37629658 Stefan Sarnowski: Kondolencje] www.nekrologi.net, accessed 2015-05-01</ref>) was a Polish philosopher working as professor at [[Kazimierz Wielki University in Bydgoszcz]].

== Biography ==
Stefan Sarnowski graduated from [[University of Warsaw]], and in 1964 obtained his [[Magister (degree)|magister degree]] for the work ''Marksizm i darwinizm w etyce Kautskiego'' ([[Marxism]] and Darwinism in [[Karl Kautsky|Kautski]]’s ethics), with [[Marek Fritzhand]]<ref>There is an article about him [[:pl:Marek Fritzhand|in the Polish Wikipedia]].</ref> being the [[Supervisor#Science|supervisor]]. After receiving his doctorate, Stefan Sarnowski started working as adjunct at the same university.

